---
import img1 from '../assets/[4] Product Imagery & Video/iStock-1276569663.jpg';
import img2 from '../assets/[4] Product Imagery & Video/iStock-2203624688.jpg';
---

<section class="bg-[#1A1816] px-[10px] pt-24">
  <div class="bg-[#22201E] rounded-3xl pt-32 pb-32 px-[10px]">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <!-- Heading -->
      <div class="text-center mb-5" data-animate>
        <h2 class="font-fraunces text-cream text-[clamp(48px,6vw,80px)] leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Built for the clinics shaping<br />modern healthcare.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-[560px] mx-auto mb-16" data-animate data-delay="1">
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-base leading-[1.6]">
          Whether you prescribe compounds, peptides, or wellness protocols,<br class="hidden md:block" />
          we handle the operational complexity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Two-Column Cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6" data-animate data-delay="2">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-5 aspect-[4/3]">
            <img src={img1.src} alt="Aesthetic & Wellness Clinics" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-inter text-cream font-bold text-lg mb-2 px-4">
            Aesthetic &amp; Wellness Clinics
          </h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm leading-[1.6] px-4">
            Manage weight loss, peptides, and hormone protocols with automated refill cycles and pricing transparency. Streamline complex compound workflows and pharmacy payments for med spas and longevity practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-5 aspect-[4/3]">
            <img src={img2.src} alt="Physical Medicine & Collaborative Care" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-inter text-cream font-bold text-lg mb-2 px-4">
            Physical Medicine &amp; Collaborative Care
          </h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm leading-[1.6] px-4">
            Optimize pain management and rehab workflows for chiropractors while enabling seamless collaboration between prescribing providers and non-prescribing clinicians like PTs, coaches, and nutritionists.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-center pt-24 pb-8" data-animate>
      <span class="font-fraunces text-teal text-[80px] leading-none block -mb-4">&ldquo;</span>
      <blockquote class="font-fraunces text-cream text-[clamp(24px,3vw,40px)] leading-[1.35] font-normal mb-12">
        The pricing transparency alone is worth it. We're saving $2-4k/month by comparing compound options across pharmacies before prescribing. That used to be impossible.
      </blockquote>

      <p class="font-fraunces text-cream text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">
        Dr. Ryan Jacobs
      </p>
      <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">
        Founder, Revive Longevity Clinic
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
